message.body: Hi! Ah I'm so out of shape but tomorrow is the only day I'm free so I'd love to do yoga with you and Christy if that's okay!
Yes of course!! And don't worry, the class is for all levels! They rent mats for $3 I think if you don't have one, and I would def bring a towel. I try to get there by 6 to get a good spot..
Okay! How's the parking situation there?
There's tons of metered spots on 40th and on chesapeake..40th might be full but chesapeake is usually pretty wide open!
Sorry I never responded to this, I will be there :)
No worries!! And yayy!! Also, I'm not sure I'd mere mentioned anything about this to you yet, but I have a box of bridal shower stuff to give to you :-)
Okay! She didn't mention it but awesome!
Okay, sorry to be dumping it on you!!
Haha that's okay, do I just keep it with me til Meredith gets here?
Yep, she'll know what to do with it :-)
Oh, in case you need it, the code to enter the building is 7777*
Okay! Finding parking now. Do you have to pay on Chesapeake?
I think even in the evenings but I could be wrong
Oh, then I guess only until 630! Yayy
Ok I just put 2 hrs on in case. See you soon!!
